## 작업별 권장 참조 순서

- **백엔드 API/모듈/DB**  
  `agent/spec/backend_architecture_spec.md` → `agent/guidelines/spec_driven_development_guidelines.md` → `agent/schema.md` → `agent/openapi_spec.yaml` → `agent/proposal.md`

- **OAuth/인증 (백엔드 주도)**  
  `agent/guidelines/oauth_implementation_guidelines.md` → `agent/spec/backend_architecture_spec_producer.md` (1.3) → `agent/openapi_spec.yaml` → `agent/spec/frontend_architecture_spec.md` (3.1)

- **프론트엔드 페이지/라우팅**  
  `agent/spec/frontend_architecture_spec.md` (특히 §2 페이지 구조 및 라우팅 맵) → `agent/screen_flowchart.mermaid` (화면 전환·탭 흐름 확인) → `agent/guidelines/spec_driven_development_guidelines.md` → `agent/guidelines/frontend_development_guidelines.md` → `agent/openapi_spec.yaml` → `agent/proposal.md`

- **데이터·엔티티·스키마**  
  `agent/schema.md` → `agent/spec/backend_architecture_spec.md` → `agent/openapi_spec.yaml`

- **전체 시스템 구조·배포**  
  `agent/architecture.mermaid` → `agent/proposal.md` → `agent/spec/backend_architecture_spec.md` / `agent/spec/frontend_architecture_spec.md` (지침은 `agent/guidelines/` 내 해당 문서 참고)

- **기획·스택·배포 정책**  
  `agent/proposal.md` → `agent/architecture.mermaid`

- **Figma (MCP)**  
  `agent-docs-figma.mdc` 참고.

- **UI/UX·디자인 원칙 적용**  
  `agent/design/design_principle.json`(터치 타겟 44px, WCAG 2.1 AA, 반응형 브레이크포인트, LCP/FID/CLS·번들 예산, 레이아웃·챗봇 톤 등)
  `agent/design/design_tokens.json`(컬러/타이포/스페이싱/레이아웃 등 토큰 정의)
